channel.title: Help please cant publish my server
channel.description: hey guys i got an rscalifornia v2 source and i cannot seem to host this server because when i go to client and change ip to my no-ip the client stops at checking updates 1% but when i put it on the local network ip it works and i need to publish it and btw i port forwarded i have an orange livebox please help i got skype :lord3180 and if u can help on teamview just please help thnx

item.title: Help please cant publish my server
item.dc:creator: @LearningToCode1 LearningToCode1
item.description:
@LearningToCode1 wrote:

Checking Update’s is the cache…, Try finding the cache folder somewhere inside of your files or local disk C: and then, Pack it into a zipped file, Upload to dropbox and then post the new cache link inside of your auto-downloader… Then this might solve your problem’s, Also try searching on google or youtube first, They have way more thing’s that could help you before making a help thread on here.
